# Host-based rewrites: each imprint domain serves its own subfolder transparently.
# The URL in the browser stays as the imprint domain (dropthorn.com, etc.).
# Status 200! = rewrite (URL preserved). Without the !, it would be a 301 redirect.

# Dropthorn Press
/*  /dropthorn-press/:splat  200!  Host=dropthorn.com
/*  /dropthorn-press/:splat  200!  Host=www.dropthorn.com

# Neural Nexus Press
/*  /neural-nexus-press/:splat  200!  Host=neuralnexuspress.com
/*  /neural-nexus-press/:splat  200!  Host=www.neuralnexuspress.com

# Bright Haven Publishing
/*  /bright-haven-publishing/:splat  200!  Host=brighthavenpublishing.xyz
/*  /bright-haven-publishing/:splat  200!  Host=www.brighthavenpublishing.xyz
